tifunction atms  the selfserv  series is the most recent addition to the family and consists of robust range of multifunctional atms completing our selfserv portfolio selfserv  series core values transform branch transformation and improving the customer experience are at the heart of ncr’s selfserv  series for consumers the atm interface now supports multitouch and is enabled for many other omnichannel interactions these atms transform the selfservice channel by putting the personal touch back into banking through fully configurable interactive and assisted service capabilities along with modern design and aesthetics the selfserv  series enables you to connect with consumers the way they prefer anywhere anytime attract these atms help financial institutions project a positive brand image through design features such as dynamic colour leds and customizable branding panels additionally ncr’s market leading software delivers highly personalized and efficient experiences for consumers leveraging the power of ncr connections software to deliver highlydifferentiated and personalized experiences with tailored marketing and promotional offers at the atm manage the selfserv  series enables financial institutions to manage atm networks with intelligence and efficiency ncr understands the importance of managing your network and we offer the right solutions and processes to help you improve the performance of your entire atm network the selfserv  series enables faster fault detection and resolution and features state of health indicators across all media handling  devices allowing you to improve performance and manage risk while reducing costs engage the selfserv  series atms give you the power to engage and build connections that create experiences for consumers the design and aesthetics of the selfserv  series have been combined with enhanced interactivity using multitouch capabilities ncr gives you the power to shift to new interaction and authentication models at the atm such as multitouch contactless and mobile prestaging which support the omnichannel mobilefirst customer these atms also allow you to tailor your marketing messaging based on the individual preferences of the consumer location and timebased targeted marketing allows you to engage with your customers on a new level available your atms must be available at all times customers today are convenience and time oriented they expect to access their financial institution whenever and wherever they want many of the selfserv  series atms offer an increase in cassette capacity as well as deposit and dispense size to ensure your network can serve your customers where and when they demand the selfserv  series features s dispenser  designed to provide greater cash capacity and higher reliability at the atm gbxx module  to drive performance improvements and uptime in the area of recycling sdm  designed to deliver fast and simplified mixed media deposit in a single transaction with great mixed media handing standards secure security is a major concern for every bank customer the selfserv  series has security designed in to respond to the latest threats the flush infinity glass enhances security against skimming attacks using pictureinpicture technology on the  screen increases the customers awareness of what is going on around them enabling contactless via cards or smart phones on the selfserv  series can eliminate the threat of card skimming entirely these features  when combined with ncr security software  allow ncrs  series to protect you and your customers selfserv family the ncr selfserv family is the world’s most complete atm portfolio and number  brand with over  installs around the globe a configurable range of dispense deposit and recycling atms designed to future proof your investment these atms are the enabling platform to selfservice reinvention and modernization for retail banks the newest addition to the range is the ncr selfserv  series atm family aimed at the growing p