is a main concern  ·         the company is continuing to virtualize their servers ·         in the process of upgrading their software ·         the company is also upgrading their servers ·         outsourcing it structure ·         the department is primarily divided between alpharetta ga its former headquarters in dayton oh and its current headquarters in duluth ga ·         ncr corporation ‘s it department is primarily responsible for supporting the companys enterprise it functions such as applications security architecture strategy and workgroup services ·         employees in the companys workgroup services group handle data integration and operations with the companys vmware server infrastructure ·         additional infrastructure responsibilities are handled by the network communication services group which oversees field services and mobile device management ·         the companys help desk and call center handle technical issues and additional network support it vendors ·         the company uses cisco systems meetingplace to allow remotely located executives to collaborate with staff in virtual office settings ·         in august  ncr corporation acquired radiant systems inc merging the two companies and subsequently the infrastructure and systems ·         as of february  ncr corporation has finalized its purchase and acquisition of retalix  it intelligence snippets  ·        outsourcing security improvements and byod sector industry technology computer hardware technology computer services employees  revenue b fye  breaking news on investment signals date type inside scoop  spending trend topic marketing content management company ncr corporation duluth ga opportunity a midlevel source has indicated that content management solutions are a spending priority the organization uses contingentcontract workers for technology initiatives  project scoop topic software company ncr corporation duluth ga opportunity is focusing on creating its user experience us